data.description: You must see this one of a kind  home with many upgrades. Located in an outstanding community in this very quiet neighborhood in Cramac Plantation. No HOA. The breathtaking landscaping and lots of privacy. Family and friends can enjoy the nice deck in the big backyard. Remarkable features this open concept for entertaining guests. An inspiring kitchen features of Massive Chef's Kitchen with a quartz  counter tops. Beautiful bay windows and plenty of natural light. 2  gorgeous fireplace. Hardwood floors in the entire house. 4 bedrooms and 2 full bathroom plus bonus room upstairs. Can be use for an office or gaming room. There is a huge unfinished basement with lots of potential. What are you waiting for?
